items.title: US top doctor calls for cancer warnings on alcohol
items.description: Surgeon General Vivek Murthy says warning labels should be updated to increase awareness of links to seven types of cancer.

items.title: Biden blocks Japan's Nippon Steel from buying US Steel
items.description: Biden decided to scrap the deal despite concerns that it could damage Washington's relations with Tokyo.

items.title: Israel confirms it is holding Gaza hospital chief Abu Safiya
items.description: The IDF had earlier told a local NGO it was unaware of his case, sparking concern.

items.title: Why is it so hard to arrest South Korea's  impeached president?
items.description: Yoon Suk Yeol has been impeached by parliament and suspended from office.

items.title: Apple to pay $95m to settle Siri 'listening' lawsuit
items.description: The tech giant denies wrongdoing after being accused of eavesdropping on customers.
